<!--This page shows the home screen, gives a brief overview of the web app, then gives a link
    for the user to start a new quiz.-->

<body style="background-color: black; font-size: x-large;">
    <div style="position: relative; text-align: center;">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/theater2.jpeg" style=" height: 98%; width: 100%;  " a>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4"></div>
            <div class="container-fluid text-centered col-4" style="position:absolute; top: 30% ; left: 50% ; transform: translate(-50%, -30%);font-size:2vw ">
                <p>Welcome!</p>
                <p>This web app lets you take a short quiz about movies.  Given a movie plot, you have to guess which movie it is.  Have fun!</p><br />
               
